我们有DNA报告  我在实验室里有关系

422
00:33:40,600 --> 00:33:42,640
He gave me the file without the others knowing.
他把文件给了我，其他人都不知道

423
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:45,800
Run it against the DNA of 80 million people.
