00:34:01,080 --> 00:34:03,840
- Mister Hamza Kaymak. - Yes, that's his name.
-哈姆萨·凯马克先生  -是的  就是他

430
00:34:04,440 --> 00:34:08,760
- He's a fugitive. Escaped from prison. - I know. Because I arranged it.
