448
00:35:10,680 --> 00:35:12,960
You know what we were just talking about, Zuhal?
你知道我们在说什么吗，祖哈尔？

449
00:35:13,040 --> 00:35:15,960
Why do you think he lowered his gun when he saw you?
为什么看到你时他会放下枪？

450
00:35:17,200 --> 00:35:19,360
He didn't want to kill you. He was here for me.
他不想杀了你  他是冲我来的

451
00:35:20,200 --> 00:35:21,480
