465
00:36:03,280 --> 00:36:06,280
Thieves drive me up the walls.
小偷把我逼疯了

466
00:36:07,680 --> 00:36:11,560
If he came to us, telling us needed help, we would've given him everything.
如果他来找我们，告诉我们他需要帮助，我们会尽力帮助他

467
00:36:12,320 --> 00:36:14,560
